flowchart LR
  IA[Identity Authority] --> EI[Eligibility Issuer]
  EI --> VC[Anonymous Vote Token]
  VC --> BBX[Ballot Box]
  Client[Voting Client] -->|Encrypted ballot| BBX
  BBX --> Board[Bulletin Board]
  Board --> Merkle[Merkle Root]
  Board --> Reasoning[Formal Reasoning Layer]
  Board --> Audit[Heuristic Audit Engine]
  Board --> Tally[Tally Authority]
  Reasoning --> Proof[Proof Logs]
  Audit --> Findings[Audit Findings]
  Tally --> Result[Verifiable Result]
